            and Governance (decision-making).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>ðŸ” Attack Simulation</h3>
          <p class="meta">Security Modeling</p>
          <p>
            Modeling adversarial scenarios with realistic threat actors (financial attackers, organized crime, 
            state-sponsored) and economic constraints.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>ðŸ“Š Comparative Analysis</h3>
          <p class="meta">Protocol Evaluation</p>
